highlights.text: Mrs. GREEN APPLE has the most spots on Top Songs Japan. “ライラック” is the highest at #2.
“君はロックを聴かない” by Aimyon has been on Top Songs Japan the longest, at 2703 days straight.
“JUMP” by BLACKPINK is the highest new entry on Top Songs Japan at #18.
“Winter Ahead (with PARK HYO SHIN)” by V and Park Hyo Shin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Japan, up 46 spots at #117.
